{"talk":{"id":14485,"name":"Heidi M. Sosik: The discoveries awaiting us in the ocean's twilight zone","description":"What will we find in the twilight zone: the vast, mysterious, virtually unexplored realm hundreds of meters below the ocean's surface? Heidi M. Sosik of Woods Hole Oceanographic Institution wants to find out. In this wonder-filled talk, she shares her plan to investigate these uncharted waters, which may hold a million new species and 90 percent of the world's fish biomass, using submersible technology. What we discover there won't just astound us, Sosik says -- it will help us be better stewards of the world's oceans. (This ambitious idea is part of the Audacious Project, TED's initiative to inspire and fund global change.)","slug":"heidi_m_sosik_the_discoveries_awaiting_us_in_the_ocean_s_twilight_zone","recorded_at":"2018-04-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-06-08 14:40:39","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:43:45","viewed_count":1227717,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":494,"name":"TED2018"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/fab1efb51c42cc42de1a65ec7eb9e078a44c2ef5_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/fab1efb51c42cc42de1a65ec7eb9e078a44c2ef5_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/fab1efb51c42cc42de1a65ec7eb9e078a44c2ef5_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/fab1efb51c42cc42de1a65ec7eb9e078a44c2ef5_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/41245da655d6166c7128edbba126ab4bf0f17c64_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HeidiMSosik_2018-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":4952887,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HeidiMSosik_2018-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":13724142,"mime